    <briefdescription>
<para>Decorator that catches specified key events and forwards them to a listener. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class wraps any element and intercepts key presses matching the specified keys. When a matching key is pressed, it invokes the listener with an event callback.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Base element type to decorate </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>KEYS</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Key codes to catch (variadic template parameters) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
